`` <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">The proposal , while well - intended</COREF> , <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">I</COREF> think can be dangerously misleading because the likely consequence would be to weaken , rather than strengthen the control <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">the SEC</COREF> has exercised for 50 years over the financial adequacy and viability of broker - dealers , '' <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">Michael Raoul - Duval , managing director of <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">First Boston</COREF> ,</COREF> said in an interview .
